thread.title: David

author: David
title: David
text: Thank you TapeOnline for carrying the double disc Unikeep CD Safety-Sleeves. You are one of the few that carry them. MicroCenter stopped, Best buy stopped. You price is competitive ($15/100), but your shipping at $10.99 cost almost as much as 100 of the sleeves. and If I had bought only 73 sleeves, the shipping would cost more than the sleeves. USPS small box flat rate priority mail costs just $6.45 on a commercial account like you.
